人气韩星猛男组合RANA & TARZAN｜KPOP之夜
內容：
[星期五 1月31日] 人气韩星猛男组合RANA & TARZAN｜KPOP之夜今年 1 月，韩国超人 RANA 和 TARZAN 强势回归，我们将为您带来精彩表演！前韩国流行歌手 RANA（来自 Nine Muses）在第 17 届韩国超级模特大赛中夺冠后声名鹊起，自 2014 年以来一直称霸 DJ 界。凭借其标志性的“In My Days”风格，她曾点燃韩国世界 DJ 节和韩国泥浆节等音乐节，现在她准备再次点亮澳门。与她一起登场的是韩国劲旅 TARZAN（又名 Kuntac），其首张单曲“More’s Place”在 Beatport 的 Chill-out 排行榜上排名第 14。这位多才多艺的 DJ 和健美运动员还获得了多项荣誉，例如 The Bloody Beetroots 混音大赛第二名和 Muscle Mania 拉斯维加斯锦标赛前 10 名。不要错过 2025 年 1 月 31 日星期五在 Club MOP 首尔星期五活动中举行的 RANA 和 TARZAN 现场表演——一个不容错过的 K-beats 和高能量氛围之夜！[FRI 31 JAN] Club MOP presents RANA & TARZANThis January, we're turning up the heat with the electrifying return of Korean sensations RANA and TARZAN!Former K-pop star RANA from Nine Muses, who skyrocketed to fame after winning 1st place in the 17th Korea Super Model contest, has been dominating the DJ world since 2014. With her signature “In My Days” style, she’s ignited festivals like World DJ Festival Korea and Mud Festival Korea, and now she’s ready to light up Macau once again.Joining her is Korean powerhouse TARZAN, aka Kuntac, whose debut single “More’s Place” hit #14 on Beatport’s Chill-out chart. This multi-talented DJ and bodybuilder also boasts accolades like 2nd place in The Bloody Beetroots’ remix contest and Top 10 at the Muscle Mania Las Vegas Championship.Don’t miss RANA & TARZAN live at Club MOP’s Seoul Fridays event on Fri 31 January 2025—an unmissable night of K-beats and high-energy vibes!
门票包含两杯饮品Entry Fee includes 2 Drinks
